metadata.simpleText:
Hi! I'm Anastasia, I live in St.Petersburg, Russia. I love languages and I like to help those who chose to learn Russian (one of the most beautiful languages). Welcome to this journey! ❤️

Watch, comment and if you like my lessons share with friends! 

Thank you so much!
